Rym: You made that kid's day.

113
00:05:12,691 --> 00:05:13,820
Rym: He's been waiting.

114
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:15,264
Scott: Yeah, we played some Dr.

115
00:05:15,304 --> 00:05:18,478
Scott: Mario, and they were really fucking good, but I'm also really good at Dr.

116
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:18,820
Scott: Mario.

117
00:05:18,940 --> 00:05:21,640
Scott: But not, you know, super good, but better than everyone else I know.

118
00:05:22,841 --> 00:05:27,440
Scott: And, you know, it was close, I lost, and then it was close, I won, and then it was close, I lost.

119
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,142
Scott: And it was like,

120
00:05:28,162 --> 00:05:28,584
Scott: "Alright.".

121
00:05:28,685 --> 00:05:31,758
Scott: But then it's like, even though it was close, I'm like, "I'm done with

122
00:05:31,798 --> 00:05:31,959
Scott: this.".

123
